Pre-Game Insights: Senegal, as the defending champion, aims to continue their successful streak in AFCON with a win against Guinea.
Guinea has shown fighting spirit with a draw against Cameroon and a win against Gambia under coach Kaba Diawara.
Miscellaneous Highlights: The match is held in Cote d'Ivoire and can be viewed on Sky Sports Main Event, Premier League, and Ultra HDR.
